                    >
                        üîë Usar c√≥digo de backup de emerg√™ncia
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="backup-help" class="hidden mt-4 p-4 bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 border border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-700 rounded-lg">
                        <h5 class="font-bold text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-200 mb-2 text-sm">
                            üìã C√≥digos de Backup
                        </h5>
